data.title: British Comedy Guide
meta_keywords: Rob Brydon British comedy work Actor Writer Executive producer Stand-up comedian Presenter Script editor
data.meta_description: Rob Brydon is a 59-year-old Welsh actor, writer, executive producer, stand-up comedian, presenter and script editor, known for Gavin & Stacey, Would I Lie To You?, The Rob Brydon Show, Rob Brydon's Annually Retentive, The Trip, The Keith Barret Show, Marion And Geoff and Human Remains.
